  "prompt": "What are some AngularJS interview questions?",
  "response": "Here are some common AngularJS interview questions:\n\n1. Basic Conceptual Questions:\n```\n- What is AngularJS?\n- What are the key features of AngularJS?\n- Explain the MVC architecture in AngularJS\n- What is two-way data binding?\n- What are directives in AngularJS?\n```\n\n2. Scope and Controller Questions:\n```\n- What is $scope in AngularJS?\n- What is the difference between $scope and controller?\n- Explain controller as syntax\n- How do you share data between controllers?\n```\n\n3. Directive-related Questions:\n```\n- What are the types of directives?\n- How do you create a custom directive?\n- Explain the different directive restrict options\n- What are the directive lifecycle hooks?\n```\n\n4. Service and Dependency Injection:\n```\n- What are services in AngularJS?\n- Explain different types of services\n- How does dependency injection work?\n- What is the difference between factory and service?\n```\n\n5. Advanced Concept Questions:\n```\n- What is digest cycle?\n- How does two-way data binding work internally?\n- Explain $watch and $apply\n- What are providers in AngularJS?\n```\n\n6. Technical Implementation Questions:\n```\n- How do you optimize AngularJS performance?\n- What are routing techniques in AngularJS?\n- How do you handle HTTP requests?\n- Explain promise and $q service\n```\n\n7. Practical Scenario Questions:\n```\n- How would you implement form validation?\n- How do you handle error scenarios?\n- Demonstrate communication between components\n```\n\n8. Comparison and Conceptual Questions:\n```\n- Differences between AngularJS and Angular\n- Pros and cons of AngularJS\n- When would you choose AngularJS?\n```\n\n9. Code-based Questions:\n```\n- Write a custom directive\n- Implement a service\n- Create a controller with specific functionality\n```\n\n10. Best Practices:\n```\n- How do you structure an AngularJS application?\n- What are common performance pitfalls?\n- How do you organize large applications?\n```\n\nSample Code Examples:\n\n1. Simple Controller:\n```javascript\napp.controller('UserController', function($scope) {\n  $scope.name = 'John Doe';\n  $scope.greet = function() {\n    alert('Hello ' + $scope.name);\n  };\n});\n```\n\n2. Custom Directive:\n```javascript\napp.directive('customDirective', function() {\n  return {\n    restrict: 'EA',\n    template: '<div>Custom Directive</div>',\n    link: function(scope, element, attrs) {\n      // Directive logic\n    }\n  };\n});\n```\n\n3. Service Example:\n```javascript\napp.service('UserService', function($http) {\n  this.getUsers = function() {\n    return $http.get('/api/users');\n  };\n});\n```\n\nTips for Interview Preparation:\n- Understand core concepts thoroughly\n- Practice coding examples\n- Know the internal working of AngularJS\n- Be prepared to discuss real-world scenarios\n- Understand performance implications\n\nRecommended Study Areas:\n- AngularJS documentation\n- Advanced JavaScript concepts\n- Design patterns\n- Performance optimization techniques\n\nRemember that interviews may vary in depth and focus, so being versatile in your knowledge is key.\n\nWould you like me to elaborate on any of these topics or provide more detailed explanations of specific concepts?",
